1. *Platila* sam račun u restoranu. (I paid the bill at the restaurant.)
2. Ona *platila* svoju kartu za koncert. (She paid for her concert ticket.)
3. Kada *platite* račun, dobićete popust. (When you pay the bill, you will receive a discount.)
4. Nisam još *platila* kiriju ovog meseca. (I haven't paid the rent for this month yet.)
5. *Platili* smo skupe karte za let. (We paid for expensive flight tickets.)
6. Moram da *platim* kaznu za prebrzu vožnju. (I have to pay a fine for speeding.)
7. Da li ste *platili* članarinu za teretanu? (Did you pay the gym membership fee?)
8. *Platite* ovu kupovinu na kasi. (Pay for this purchase at the cash register.)
9. Koliko je tvoja firma *platila* za ovaj oglas? (How much did your company pay for this advertisement?)
10. Ako *platite* unapred, dobićete dodatni popust. (If you pay in advance, you will receive an additional discount.)